Â…</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>

  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para>The Variable object allows you to create and name a variable and
    assign to it a real number value. A variable can be used in numerous
    commands which allows you to customize the mission sequence to your
    application. In the simplest case, a variable can be defined by a simple
    assignment to a numeric literal. In more complex cases, a variable can be
    defined using an assignment that contains a complicated mathematical
    expression.</para>
  </refsection>

